7.9 Independent auditorâ€™s report on a limited assurance engagement

In a limited assurance engagement, the procedures per- formed are less extensive than in a reasonable assurance engagement, and accordingly, a substantially lower level of assurance is obtained. The selection of the assurance proce- dures is subject to the professional judgment of the auditor.

